# Coding Standards

Use: Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, TanStack Table, TanStack Virtual, Framer Motion, React Hook Form, Zod, React Query, Zustand, Drizzle ORM, Supabase.

- Custom hooks for reusable logic
- Zod schemas for validation
- Server Actions / Route Handlers for mutations
- Never expose SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY in client or Tauri bundle
